表格机器周期记录的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('tblMachineCyleLog')
and type = 'U')
drop table tblMachineCyleLog
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: tblMachineCyleLog */
/*==============================================================*/
create table tblMachineCyleLog (
ID int null,
DispatchNo varchar(30) not null,
MouldNo varchar(30) null,
MachineNo varchar(30) null,
EndDate datetime not null,
LastCycle int null,
ThisCycle int null,
CreateDate datetime null,
constraint PK_TBLMACHINECYLELOG primary key (DispatchNo, EndDate)
)
go

declare @CurrentUser sysname
select @CurrentUser = user_name()
execute sp_addextendedproperty 'MS_Description',
'机器周期更新记录表',
'user', @CurrentUser, 'table', 'tblMachineCyleLog'
go
